title: Carrot and Walnut Cake
ingredients: ['375g plain flour', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '3 teaspoons baking powder', '6 eggs', '250ml vegetable oil', '175g icing sugar', '125g chopped walnuts', '100g grated carrots', '250ml milk', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '2 teaspoons ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '1/2 teaspoon ground cardamom']
